{
  "stem": "766.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't want to see the faces, how they hated us, looking at us and treating us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I was young, and I was rebelling.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew there were political, other excesses against Jews when there was independence of Poland, 1918.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There came nationalistic movements, so there were pogroms and other things, and I remembered that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also, I was never, ever hurt by anybody, hit by anybody, but others were hit, other Jews who were wearing the-- the-- the religious thing.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But not I, personally, but I was aware of what's going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't talk so much about this, but I knew it, and everybody felt the same way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody felt it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There wasn't like now, you sit with parents and discuss, but they felt it too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure, they felt it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They felt it double, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As Russian Jews, they felt the-- the non-- the Orthodox, the local Jews thought that they are not Jews because they were not so religious.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in appearance, [LAUGHS] they thought they are half Jews or not Jews at all, so they have to struggle with them too, but it is just nothing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when the time came, I was admitted over there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the [NON-ENGLISH] Matura, this was enough to be admitted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later, when I was as a student, I had to pass examination, but entry was no.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't run away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe not.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later, she-- she was proud, on one hand, but she was a Jewish mother, so it's understood.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who, I?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very little.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had, in school, French, but you know, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I came to France, I mixed up bonjour and au revoir.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mixed it up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it came with gradually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, a couple hours.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
